text: In lex fridmans recent interview with Jaron Lanier, Lanier mentions a combination of Tik tok and github as a possible future collaboration Method. Spontaneous yet deep and valuable collaboration. He also shares nuanced and insightful perspectives on topics like AI, algorithms, crypto/blockchain and government/politics (perpetual annoyance - I love it :heart:) HIghly recommend!  <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fx0G6DHMfXM>
